            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_c988fc21ff",
              "flowId": "flow:p6",
              "nodeId": "p6:n7"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "”。相关数据仅在本地处理。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "featureId": "ui_HomePage_03ad5d65fc",
        "tokens": [
          {
            "text": "当您点击开始或停止按钮以控制计步任务时，我们会收集您的"
